## LOYIHA

SavdoAI — O'zbekiston savdogarlari uchun AI-powered savdo boshqaruv tizimi.
Telegram bot + FastAPI REST API + Next.js web panel + Android printer app.
PostgreSQL RLS izolyatsiya. Claude + Gemini AI. 155 Python fayl, 58 servis.

