## YANGI FUNKSIYALAR (v25.3.2a)

### 1. Excel Chat (/excel)
/excel → Excel yuborish → har qanday savol → AI javob + PDF
Fayllar: shared/services/excel_chat.py, excel_analyzer.py
         services/bot/handlers/excel_chat.py
MUHIM: /excel bosilmasa nakladnoy/reestr avvalgidek ishlaydi!
Hujjat oqimi: Excel Chat → Nakladnoy → Reestr → Oddiy

### 2. Smart AI (/savol)
/savol Salimovning qarzi qancha? → bazadan tekshirib javob
Yoki shunchaki yozish: "omborda Ariel bormi?" → avtomatik aniqlaydi
Fayl: shared/services/smart_ai.py
Xavfsizlik: SQL injection yo'q — faqat SELECT, faqat user_id filtrlangan
Sotuv oqimi bilan adashmaydi (_is_biznes_savol detektori)

### 3. Avtomatik kunlik PDF hisobot
Har kuni 09:00 Toshkent — matn + PDF avtomatik yuboriladi
/hisobot — istalgan vaqtda PDF olish
Fayl: shared/services/auto_report_pdf.py
PDF: DejaVuSans Cyrillic, ko'k header, qizil qarz jadval, MAXFIY tamg'a

### 4. 35 bug fix (audit)
33 duplikat endpoint, HMAC auth, MD5→SHA256, RLS fix,
Worker crash, WebSocket token, main.py -28%

## ENDPOINT PATTERN

@router.post("/endpoint", tags=["Guruh"])
async def endpoint(data: Sorov, uid: int = Depends(get_uid)):
    async with rls_conn(uid) as c:
        row = await c.fetchrow("INSERT INTO ... RETURNING id", uid, data.nomi)
    return dict(row)

## BOT HANDLER PATTERN

async def cmd_x(update: Update, ctx: ContextTypes.DEFAULT_TYPE):
    if not await faol_tekshir(update): return
    uid = update.effective_user.id

main.py → ilovani_qur() → register_handlers(app)
Circular import → lazy import (funksiya ichida!)

## PDF PATTERN (Cyrillic)

from shared/services/auto_report_pdf.py yoki excel_chat.py
_init_fonts() → DejaVuSans (Linux) yoki Helvetica (fallback)
_FONT / _FONT_B module-level o'zgaruvchilar

