## DB

40+ jadval, RLS: current_uid()
Asosiy: users, tovarlar, klientlar, sotuv_sessiyalar, chiqimlar,
kirimlar, qarzlar, kassa_operatsiyalar, fakturalar, nakladnoy_counter
Istisnolar RLS: shogirdlar/xarajatlar/xarajat_kategoriyalar → admin_uid

## 🚫 TAQIQLANGAN (14 qoida)

1. SELECT * yozma — faqat kerakli ustunlar
2. RETURNING * yozma
3. except: (bare) yozma — except Exception:
4. f"%{term}%" yozma — like_escape()
5. SET qoldiq = $2 absolyut yozma — GREATEST
6. get_pool() biznes queryda — rls_conn(uid)
7. parol_hash response da qaytarma
8. bot URL → NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL qo'yma
9. Test < 1564 qilma
10. TypeScript xato qoldirma
11. __import__() ishlatma — import yoz
12. hashlib.md5() tizimda — sha256 (Click.uz tashqari)
13. asyncio.get_event_loop() — asyncio.run()
14. Duplikat endpoint yaratma (main.py + routes/)

## XAVFSIZLIK (hammasi 0 bo'lishi SHART)

bare except=0 | __import__=0 | MD5 tizim=0 | SELECT *=0
eval/exec=0 | parol_hash leak=0 | user_id siz query=0

